'''NGC 1052'''是一個在[[天球|天球]]上位於[[鯨魚座|鯨魚座]]的[[橢圓星系|橢圓星系]]。

== 特徵 ==
NGC 1052距離銀河系約6300萬光年<ref name="tonryetal2001">{{cite journal| author=J. L. Tonry |display-authors=4  | author2=A. Dressler | author3=J. P. Blakeslee | author4=E. A. Ajhar | author5=A. B. Fletcher | author6=G. A. Luppino | author7=M. R. Metzger | author8=C. B. Moore  | title=The SBF Survey of Galaxy Distances. IV. SBF Magnitudes, Colors, and Distances | journal=Astrophysical Journal | date=2001 | volume=546 | number=2 | pages=681–693 | doi=10.1086/318301 | bibcode=2001ApJ...546..681T|arxiv = astro-ph/0011223 }}</ref>，並且擁有[[低電離星系核|LINER]]型[[活动星系核|活动星系核]]，這代表在NGC 1052中央有大量恆星形成的[[星暴|星暴]]現象<ref name="pierceetal2005">{{cite journal| title=The Evolutionary History of the Elliptical Galaxy NGC 1052 | journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | date=2005 | volume=358 | number=1 | pages=419–431 | doi=10.1111/j.1365-2966.2005.08778.x | bibcode=2005MNRAS.358..419P|arxiv = astro-ph/0501066 | last1=Pierce | first1=Michael | last2=Brodie | first2=Jean P | last3=Forbes | first3=Duncan A | last4=Beasley | first4=Michael A | last5=Proctor | first5=Robert | last6=Strader | first6=Jay }}</ref>，並且天文學家以更高解析度的觀測資料發現了數個[[恆星形成|恆星形成]]區域和年輕[[星團|星團]]證實了此一現象<ref name="fernandez2011">{{cite journal| author=Fernández-Ontiveros, J. A. |display-authors=4  | author2=López-Sanjuan, C. | author3=Montes, M. | author4=Prieto, M. A. | author5=Acosta-Pulido, J. A.  | title=The most recent burst of star formation in the massive elliptical galaxy NGC 1052 | journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society Letters | date=2011 | volume=411 | number=1 | pages=L21–L25 | doi=10.1111/j.1745-3933.2010.00985.x | bibcode=2011MNRAS.411L..21F| arxiv=1011.2498 }}</ref>。

NGC 1052還發現了從星系核心延伸的兩條小規模的[[相对论性喷流|噴流]]，以及比星系盤面本身延伸更遠的[[21公分線|中性氫]]盤狀結構<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ned.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/nph-datasearch?search_type=Note_id&objid=7496&objname=NGC%201052&img_stamp=YES&hconst=73.0&omegam=0.27&omegav=0.73&corr_z=1&of=table |title=Notes for NGC 1052 (NED) |accessdate=2018-09-27 |archive-date=2018-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180927125322/http://ned.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/nph-datasearch?search_type=Note_id&objid=7496&objname=NGC%201052&img_stamp=YES&hconst=73.0&omegam=0.27&omegav=0.73&corr_z=1&of=table |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這些特徵顯示在大約10億年前和富含氣體的星系{{link-en|星系合併|Galaxy merger|碰撞與合併}}產生了上述的特徵<ref name=fernandez2011 />。

== 星系中心黑洞 ==
NGC 1052中心有一個高速旋轉的[[超大質量黑洞|超大質量黑洞]]，質量約為1.54億[[太陽質量|{{solar mass}}]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Spectral analysis of the accretion flow in NGC 1052 with ''Suzaku''|work=iopscience.iop.org|url=http://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/0004-637X/698/1/528/meta|accessdate=1 April 2018}}</ref>，並且該黑洞大範圍的磁場強度為0.02到8.3 [[特斯拉|特斯拉]]。以博士生Anne-Kathrin Baczko為首的研究團隊對此指出該黑洞的磁能量足以提供前述兩道相對論性噴流的驅動能量。

NGC 1052中心超大質量黑洞的位置是除了銀河系超大質量黑洞[[人馬座A*|人馬座A*]]以外，目前已知宇宙中位置量測最精準的天體<ref>{{cite web|title=Twin jets pinpoint the heart of an active galaxy|work=phys.org|url=https://phys.org/news/2016-09-twin-jets-heart-galaxy.html|accessdate=1 April 2018|archive-date=2018-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180707231300/https://phys.org/news/2016-09-twin-jets-heart-galaxy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

